      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable daily driver that's easy on the wallet? This car is in fair condition and shows some honest character from its years on the road, but it still starts right up and handles well! It\u2019s perfect for someone who values dependable performance over a showroom finish and is looking for a solid vehicle at a great price.",
