    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior has some noticeable cosmetic issues, including a few medium-sized dents on the passenger side and some fading in the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and there is a small tear in the driver's seat, though all electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that reflects its age and usage.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
