      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and minor paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though the suspension is starting to feel soft and it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that just needs some cosmetic and mechanical attention to bring it back to its best.",
