    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a legacy of meticulous care and uncompromising ownership. It offers a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that transcends the typical pre-owned market. Experience the pinnacle of refinement in a package that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
